data.description:
Welcome to 502 W Saint Catherine Street! This 4-plex investment property is a rare opportunity to own a well-maintained, income-generating piece of real estate in the vibrant city of Louisville, Kentucky. Located in the historic Old Louisville neighborhood, this property offers four separate units, each with its own unique charm and character.
Each unit features spacious living areas, ample storage, and updated kitchens and bathrooms. Tenants will appreciate the convenience of on-site laundry facilities and off-street parking. 

Total rent monthly is $3595 each tenant paying 120 monthly for utilities.
